pageProduct.name: NutraLife Green Lipped Mussel 850mg 90 Capsules NEW
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Nutra-Life® uses only peak condition mussels grown in the pristine coastal waters of New Zealand. The mussels are grown and harvested sustainably; then processed using a unique cold-extraction Biolane™ technique to preserve the mussels. This formula includes Vitamin C, to support connective tissue and collagen formation.

Size: 90 capsules

KEY FEATURES

• New Zealand Sourced Mussels
• Contains Vitamin C to support collagen formation and connective tissue health

Warnings

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.
DERIVED FROM SEAFOOD. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Each capsule provides: Green lipped mussel dried 850mg, Ascorbic
acid (Vitamin C) 11.5mg.

Contains: Contains: Animal product, sulfites, crustacean products.

Allergen Free From: Artificial Colours| Artificial Flavours| Artificial Preservatives| Dairy| Egg| Gluten| Soy| Wheat

Directions

RECOMMENDED ADULT DOSAGE: Take 2 capsules daily with food or as directed by your healthcare professional.

USAGE INSTRUCTIONS

RECOMMENDED ADULT DOSAGE: Take 2 capsules daily with food or as directed by your healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store in a cool dry place below 30°C.
